# Platform Planning Documentation Rule

## Rule Configuration
```json
{
  "name": "Platform Planning Documentation",
  "description": "Updates documentation files based on platform planning decisions and task completion",
  "triggers": {
    "onPlanningDecision": true,
    "onArchitectureChange": true,
    "onFeaturePlanning": true,
    "onTaskCompletion": true
  },
  "actions": [
    {
      "type": "updateDocumentation",
      "files": [
        "docs/documentation-plan.md",
        "docs/llm-context.md",
        "docs/llm-integration.md"
      ],
      "updateTypes": [
        "platformDecisions",
        "architectureUpdates",
        "featurePlanning",
        "integrationStrategy",
        "implementationPlan",
        "taskCompletion"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "conditions": {
    "documentationFiles": [
      "docs/documentation-plan.md",
      "docs/llm-context.md",
      "docs/llm-integration.md"
    ]
  }
}
```

## Documentation Updates

### 1. documentation-plan.md
Update when:
- Planning:
  - System architecture changes
  - Development standards updates
  - Testing strategy modifications
  - Deployment process changes
  - Documentation structure updates
- Task Completion:
  - Architecture implementation
  - Development standard adoption
  - Testing framework setup
  - Deployment pipeline updates
  - Documentation structure implementation

### 2. llm-context.md
Update when:
- Planning:
  - LLM model selection changes
